getHeroeById
getHeroeById(id: number)
Defined in src/app/services/heroes/heroes.services.ts:30326

Simulate GET /heroes/:id

Parameters :
Name Type Optional Description
id number No

Hero ID
Example : 
Simple call
getHeroesById(300)
Returns : any

Hero that matches the id specified as parameter.

  /**
   * @ignore
   */
  constructor() {
      console.log('HeroesService::constructor() | method called');
  }

  /**
   * Simulate GET /heroes.
   *
   * @example
   * Simple call
   * getAllHeroes
   * @returns All Heroes.
   */
  getAllHeroes() {
    return this.heroes;
  }

  /**
   * Simulate GET /heroes/:id
   *
   * @example
   * Simple call
   * getHeroesById(300)
   * @param {number} id Hero ID
   * @returns Hero that matches the id specified as parameter.
   */
  getHeroeById(id: number) {
    return this.heroes
      .filter(heroe => heroe.id === id)
      .pop();
  }
